Please Read README.jis.
I wrote README.jis using jis code.
Escape sequences are:
     kanji shift-in = ESC $ @ and
     kanji shift-out = ESC ( J.
To convert README.jis to README ( shift jis code ):
     Use jconv when you read this file at SONY NEWS.
           % jconv -jI README.jis > README
     And use nkf when you read this at other machine.
           % nkf -x README.jis > README

